# 🧠 What I Understood

A string is a collection of characters.

Example:

HELLO

Characters:

H
E
L
L
O

To solve most string problems:

Take one character
⬇️
Process it
⬇️
Move to next character
⬇️
Repeat

This process is called string traversal.

