# 📚 New Concept Learned

## Uppercase and Lowercase Logic

Uppercase Letters:

A to Z

Lowercase Letters:

a to z

Example:

PyThOn

Uppercase:

P
T
O

Count = 3

Lowercase:

y
h
n

Count = 3

Learning:
- Character classification logic.

